*nonolith-connect-1.1 (22 Mar 2012)

  22 Mar 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org>
  +files/1.1-cflags-respect.patch, +nonolith-connect-1.1.ebuild:
  New upstream release which implements a REST API and adds advanced trigger
  modes for future use. Udev rule has been removed, not needed due to USB
  initial group on nonolith-connect user.

*nonolith-connect-1.0.1 (21 Feb 2012)

  21 Feb 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org>
  +files/1.0.1-cflags-respect.patch, +files/60-nonolith-connect.rules,
  +nonolith-connect-1.0.1.ebuild, +files/nonolith-connect.initd, +metadata.xml:
  Initial commit. Ebuild by me, build system tamed by Kacper "xarthisius"
  Kowalik. Please note that you require CEE hardware to use the pixelpulse
  visualiser. Many thanks to upstream for rolling me a personal tarball.

